-- Rhodia Forecasts Earnings Will Reach $1.4 Billion in Three to Five Years
-- B y   V i d y a   R o o t
-- 2010-10-04T05:12:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-04/rhodia-expects-ebita-of-more-than-1-38-billion-in-three-to-five-years.html
Rhodia SA sees earnings before
interest, taxes, depreciation and amortisation of 1 billion 
euros in three to five years. The company is setting new targets 
for the 2013-2015 period that represents growth of 40 percent
compared to 2010 expectations, the company said in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
